For the purposes of this project we need to define a few common terms. One of the most common and troublesome terms used by memebers of the restored church is &ldquo;Doctrine.&rdquo;
How We Define Doctrine Here # [!info] Docrine literally means &ldquo;teaching.&rdquo; Any current teaching of the church is therefore a &ldquo;doctrine&rdquo; of the church.
Implications: # Not every doctrine will be complete, up-to-date, or even true.
